    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Organizational Growth Pains
---
At the outset, the man takes stock of the obstacles. He does not force his
advance. He perseveres on the right course and acquires the appropriate
assistants. He continuously rechecks his bearings, as the confusion is
gradually resolved.
